| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2639 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 802e6ac4-ba60-5696-a6d2-db0729b2bdcb"
